## 🔀 FLOW PHÂN TÍCH ĐA KHUNG THỜI GIAN

```
main.py gọi strategy_engine.analyze() mỗi khi M5 có nến mới đóng:

                ┌─────────────────────────────────┐
                │       analyze() ENTRY POINT     │
                │   (kích hoạt mỗi M5 bar close)  │
                └──────────────┬──────────────────┘
                               │
                    ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                    │  [H1] Market Struct │
                    │  detect_swing_points│
                    │  + market_structure │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │ bias = BULLISH/BEARISH
                               │ (NEUTRAL → EXIT early)
                    ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                    │  [M15] FVG Scanner  │
                    │  scan_fvg() +       │
                    │  update_fvg_pool()  │
                    │  get_active_fvgs()  │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │ active_fvgs[]
                               │ (empty → EXIT early)
                    ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                    │  [M5] Price in FVG? │
                    │  check_price_in_fvg │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │ triggered_fvg
                               │ (None → EXIT early)
                    ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                    │  [M5] Pinbar valid? │
                    │  validate_pinbar()  │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │ pin_score
                               │ (False → EXIT early)
                    ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                    │  [M5] VSA Climax?   │
                    │  validate_vsa()     │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │ vsa_score
                               │ (False → EXIT early)
                    ┌──────────▼──────────────────────┐
                    │  Composite Score                 │
                    │  score = 40%pin+35%vsa+25%struct │
                    │  if score >= 0.55 → SIGNAL!      │
                    └──────────┬───────────────────────┘
                               │
                    ┌──────────▼──────────┐
                    │  Calculate Entry/SL │
                    │  → SignalResult     │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │
                               ▼
              SignalResult(direction, score, entry, sl, fvg_ref)
                               │
                               ▼
                          main.py → risk_manager → execution.py
```

